---
title: Creamy Chicken & Bacon Pasta Bake with Tomato Rounds & Cheddar Cheese
description: It’s all hands on deck, this recipe is designed to be cooked by grown-ups and kids together! Cheesy, creamy and loaded with
crispy bacon — this pasta bake is comfort food at its finest! Tender pasta is smothered in a rich, velvety sauce, topped with
golden melted cheddar, it’s the perfect balance of cosy and crave-worthy. Get ready to dig in!

*We’ve replaced the fusilli in this recipe with penne due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
